snippet.title: Space Pricks - The Blue Deltas: Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Space Pricks is an Asteroids-style shoot-em-up-meets-RPG that's inspired by true events.  Download now and join a quest to defeat the biggest PRICKS in the universe: UPPER MANAGEMENT.
----------------------------
Regroup with V and the RESISTANCE crew to blast your way through another system's prickiest of PRICKS.

Meet brand new characters, fly with even more speed, and take on another layer of UPPER MANAGEMENT!  But don't drop your guard - The Blue Deltas are right in the heart of the PRICKS' contracting hub.  You'll have to take your flying skills up a notch to make it through in one piece.

Space Pricks - The Blue Deltas is the second chapter of this space shooter saga.  Play over on Itch for free:

https://conorogames.itch.io/space-pricks

----------------------------
Follow me on Twitter for updates: https://twitter.com/ConoroGames

Or just follow me straight up on Itch: https://conorogames.itch.io/
----------------------------
Thanks for being awesome.
